      <h4 class="display-4">Why do I lose some of my eyelashes?</h4>
      <p class="lead">Due to the natural growth cycle of your lashes you will find your natural eyelashes shed every 60-90 days as new ones grows in. We recommend getting a fill every three to four weeks to fill in lashes on the new growth.</p>
