      <h4 class="display-4">Can I use eyelash growth products with my extensions?</h4>
      <p class="lead">Lash growth products that contain steroids change the composition of your lashes and accelerate your eyelash shedding cycle, therefore we cannot guarantee the outcome. Natural lash growth products containing peptides are wonderful and will have no adverse effect on the longevity of your extensions.</p>
    </div>

